1.1.name: wordpress/bmlt-tabbed-ui
1.1.description: This plugin provides a jQuery tabbed UI for the Basic Meeting List Toolbox (BMLT). You must have BMLT installed and running. Just put the shortcode into a Wordpress page to get your very own tabbed interface to BMLT. There are no settings as of yet.
